description:
18:00 - 18:30 - arrive, mingle, have some food and drink

19:05 - 19:35 Dan Jones (Customer Reliability Engineer, Jetstack) will speak on 'The Cloud Native Holy Trinity'

This talk explores the cloud native options for quickly building applications in Google Cloud, including Cloud Run, Cloud Functions, GKE and Firebase.
title: 'Building a global API gateway service' & 'The cloud native holy trinity'
